{"tid":2515740,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"艾倫由始至終都係善良嘅人","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:16.000Z","uid":320696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f69e985a446b782d075863ec3b530ec5f47f451a","tid":2515740,"uid":320696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNX8Y692rSYWXN8pN47XDbzwgKjU2oxR7pYw1cVh9npHZ?filename=RSQS92g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSQS92g.jpg&h=2f16a515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根本壓到艾倫最後一根稻草就係塔伊巴條撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得艾倫坐係度同萊納鳩up就係想聽埋塔伊巴個演講<br />\n<br />\n塔伊巴講到艾倫奪取始祖之力好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但明明就係馬萊破壞城牆先搞到艾倫同佢老豆要奪取始祖之力 冇得怨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到最後塔伊巴向帕拉迪島宣戰已經冇彎轉 帕拉迪島冇咗外交一百年 又一直比人妖魔化 係個刻唔反抗已經逃唔過滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}